<asp:Content ID="Content2" ContentPlaceHolderID="MainContent" runat="server">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="banner columns">
            <img class="resize" src="img/banner-faq.jpg" alt="" title="" />
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="main" role="main">
        <div class="container">
            
            <div class="sixteen columns">
                <div class="title bg2">
                    <h4>FAQs</h4>
                </div>
                <p class="faq_q">Q1: What is MC EduPerks?</p>
				<p class="faq_a">A: MC EduPerks is a loyalty programme brought to you by Marshall Cavendish Education, the leading publisher in Singapore. With this programme, we are able to reward our customers for trusting and using our products to achieve academic excellence.</p>
				 
				<p class="faq_q">Q2: How do I apply for the membership?</p>
				<p class="faq_a">A: Simply log on to <a href="http://www.mceduperks.com" target="_blank">www.mceduperks.com</a> and click 'sign up'.</p>
				 
				<p class="faq_q">Q3: When and how do I receive my membership card?</p>
				<p class="faq_a">A: MC EduPerks is a cardless loyalty programme. All you need to do is to sign up online and you're a proud member of MC EduPerks.</p>
				 
				<p class="faq_q">Q4: What are the privileges and benefits of being part of MC EduPerks?</p>
				<p class="faq_a">A: Members are able to convert their assessment books purchases into MC EduPerks points and redeem exclusive gifts. Members will also receive the latest news about new book launches and regular updates on activities and promotions.</p>
				
				<p class="faq_q">Q5: Will my membership expire?</p>
				<p class="faq_a">A: This is a lifetime membership specially for all our loyal customers.</p>
				 
				<p class="faq_q">Q6: Is my membership transferrable?</p>
				<p class="faq_a">A: The membership is non-transferrable.</p>
				 
				<p class="faq_q">Q7: How do I update my personal particulars?</p>
				<p class="faq_a">A: Simply click on the ‘Member’s Area’ tab and log in to update your personal particulars.</p>
				
				<p class="faq_q">Q8: How do I redeem my gifts?</p>
				<p class="faq_a">A: <a href="signup.aspx#howtoredeem">Click here</a> to find out more on how to redeem your gifts.</p>
				 
				<p class="faq_q">Q9: Must I present any documents to redeem the gifts?</p>
				<p class="faq_a">A: All collection details will be provided in the notification email. Members are required to present the email over the counter to collect the gifts. The email can either be printed out or presented on electronic display via mobile phone/tablet.</p>
				 
				<p class="faq_q">Q10: How do I earn MC EduPerks points?</p>
				<p class="faq_a">A: Simply take a clear photo of the invoice/receipt indicating the purchase of your Marshall Cavendish Education assessment books. Submit the photo via your MC EduPerks account and points will be credited after verification.</p>
				 
				<p class="faq_q">Q11: How do I check my MC EduPerks points?</p>
				<p class="faq_a">A: Simply log on to <a href="http://www.mceduperks.com" target="_blank">www.mceduperks.com</a> and click on the 'Member's Area' tab to view your points.</p>
				
				<p class="faq_q">Q12: Will my MC EduPerks points expire?</p>
				<p class="faq_a">A: All MC EduPerks points will have a validity period of one year from date of issue and are non-exchangeable for cash.</p>
				 
				<p class="faq_q">Q13: Who are the participating merchants for this programme?</p>
				<p class="faq_a">A: <a target="_blank" href="http://www.noqstore.asia">NOQ Store</a>, POPULAR, Times The Bookshop.</p>
				 
				<p class="faq_q">Q14: Are there any other platforms to access the website?</p>
				<p class="faq_a">A: We are developing mobile apps for Android and iOS and they will be launched soon.</p>
				 
				<p class="faq_q">Q15: How are the MC EduPerks points calculated and converted?</p>
				<p class="faq_a">A: For every $1 spent, you will be awarded 1 MC EduPerks point. For purchases between $1.00 and $1.49, 1 MC EduPerks point will be awarded and for purchases between $1.50 and $1.99, 2 MC EduPerks points will be awarded (GST inclusive).</p>
				
				<p class="faq_q">Q16: Are bulk purchases allowed?</p>
				<p class="faq_a">A: Bulk purchase is limited to 9 copies of the same title in a single receipt; 10 copies and above of the same title in a single receipt will not be eligible for this programme.</p>
				
				<p class="faq_q">Q17: What types of books are eligible for this programme?</p>
				<p class="faq_a">A: Only assessment books purchased from participating merchants are eligible for this programme.</p>
				
				<p class="faq_q">Q18: Is there a validity period for submission of receipts?</p>
				<p class="faq_a">A: Receipts must be submitted within 30 days from date of purchase.</p>

            </div>
        </div>
